    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚财政部长称，罗马尼亚极右翼的乌克兰威胁十分危险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/romania-s-finance-chief-vows-to-fend-off-far-right-tame-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚财政部长警告称，极右翼候选人的危险性在于，该候选人拒绝接受罗马尼亚融入欧洲的基石，并威胁在 5 月份重新安排的总统选举之前与乌克兰关系破裂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/romania-s-finance-chief-vows-to-fend-off-far-right-tame-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 05:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼通过法律设立 610 亿美元投资机构</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/indonesia-passes-law-to-create-61-billion-investment-agency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚修改了管理东南亚国家强大国有企业的法律，为成立一个管理数十亿美元国有资产的新机构奠定了法律基础，同时寻求在国内和潜在的海外投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/indonesia-passes-law-to-create-61-billion-investment-agency</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 03:20:52 GMT</pubDate>
